secondaryOutcome.outcome:
Proportion of participants who develop respiratory failure (of any cause) requiring mechanical ventilation (invasive or noninvasive) or all-cause mortality through Day 28. - Participants will be considered to have an event if either condition is met:
Participant develops a respiratory failure (of any cause) requiring mechanical ventilation (invasive or noninvasive) or;
Participant dies prior to or on Day 28
